        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
            Ready to Find Your Perfect Freelancer?
